Website checker,

written in PHP5, based on Zeta Components
allows you to add your own tests & benchmarks extending the exsisting tests. 
GNU Affero GPL'd.

Feel free to fork it on github : https://github.com/ronanguilloux/rgWebCheck

Licence compatibility : 
